snippet.title: National police lobbying group sues Ford
snippet.description:
* A national police organization filed a lawsuit against the Ford Motor Co. Wednesday seeking the automaker to disclose modifications it is making to its Crown Victoria cars.
http://www.cnn.com/2003/LAW/01/30/crown.victoria.lawsuit/index.html

snippet.title: Trooper's death renews safety fears about Crown Victorias
snippet.description:
* City and police officials across the country are concerned about the safety of the Ford Crown Victoria after accidents that have killed or injured law enforcement officers in several states, including a New York state trooper who died last week.
http://www.cnn.com/2002/US/12/27/crown.victoria.safety/index.html

snippet.title: Union urges troopers to stay out of patrol cars
snippet.description:
* The union representing New York state troopers and state police Thursday urged its members to refuse to drive Ford Crown Victoria patrol cars until the vehicles are retrofitted to protect the fuel tanks from being punctured in crashes.
http://www.cnn.com/2003/US/Northeast/01/02/crown.victoria.safety/index.html
